Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:23.93,PS,,0,0,0,,{\c&H756575&\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs48\b0\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(543.637,410.267)\blur1}和繪畫教室的朋友們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:23.93,PS,,0,0,0,,{\c&H756575&\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs48\b0\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur1\pos(520.082,462.267)}在澀谷的宮下公園附近
